snippet.title: [Verified] "ORBJECT" by Mulpan (XXL Demon) | Geometry dash 2.11
snippet.description:
‚ñº Original song version ‚ñº
https://youtu.be/NNqaaxB04Mg

**

I was actually really excited to see the showcase of the level "Limbo" when I was serving in the military. Because I really liked the atmosphere and concept of the level. I particularly liked the song, and then an interesting concept came to mind and I started building it right after I was discharged from the military. I made the atmosphere similar to "Limbo", but I put a lot of effort into making the other elements different. I didn't have much time to complete creating the level because the level is over 3 minutes long, and I was fully concentrating on youtube during that time. But finally the level was completed in about 5 months.

The concept of the level is unique objects of the game such as orbs, portals, and pads so I think there would be a lot of bugs. (sorry about it)
A total of 37000+ objects were used, less than 40,000 objects. The difficulty could be around Insane Demon.

I started this confidently, but I feel shame that I didn't finish it properly because I was pressed for time.
But creating this level was quite fun, and it was an interesting experience.
Thanks for looking at my level!

(Translation help: Rigel)

**

~Level~
"ORBJECT" by Mulpan (Insane Demon?)

~Inspired Level~
